Event_Description: Fringing reef, sand areas with coral knolls, and segmented reef patches.
Coral reef close to oil jetty
Coral reef close to oil jetty

Fringing coral reef near the port. the site is where the oil jetty is for the trans-Israel pipeline. there are 2 jetty's there, one is not used already for a long time and the other one is rarely used. we put the ARMS in the reef area closer to the 1st jetty.
